defaultANCEFA envisions a 
defaultLiterate and Empowered Africa
default where Quality Education For All is a reality enjoyed by all children, youth and adults, without any hindrances whatsoever. In order to realize its
default dream, ANCEFA’s mandate is to enhance capacity of African Civil Society to efficiently and effectively push for universal access to quality education and development through campaign, advocacy, networking, research and resource mobilization.
